LOGOUT SCRIPT (PHP): logout script and redirections between pages

In the file "logout.php":
- Create a script whose task will be to log out the user, and then redirect to the home page.

In the app navigation: 
- Naming and linking the "Logout" element is the "logout.php" script.

Redirections: 
In the file "login.php":
- If the user is logged in, he will be redirected to the "dashboard.php" file after accessing the "loginform.php" file.

In the file "dashboard.php":
- Set redirection - if a non-logged-in user enters the address "/dashboard.php" he will be redirected to the page "/index.php".



